'''甲基绿'''（CI 42585）是和[[煌绿|煌绿]]相关的[[染色_(生物学)|染色]][[阳离子|阳离子]]，后者早在19世纪就用于对[[DNA|DNA]]染色。<ref>{{cite book|vauthors=Carnoy JB|title=La biologie cellulaire, étude comparée de la cellule dans les deux règnes / par le chanoine J.B. Carnoy...|date=1884|publisher=J. Van In|location=Bibliothèque nationale de France, département Sciences et techniques, 8-S-6259|page=148|url=http://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/bpt6k486072j|access-date=3 November 2017|archive-date=2022-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220214133845/https://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/bpt6k486072j|dead-url=no}}</ref>它一直作为经典Unna-Pappenheim染色的一部分用于染色[[细胞核|细胞核]]，也用于细胞核的{{le|对比染色|Counterstain}}。

近年来，甲基绿与DNA结合时的[[荧光|荧光]]性质<ref>{{cite web|title=fluorophores.org|url=http://www.fluorophores.tugraz.at/substance/1228|website=www.fluorophores.tugraz.at|access-date=8 August 2016|archive-date=2020-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200706150137/http://www.fluorophores.tugraz.at/substance/1228|dead-url=no}}</ref>使其可用于活细胞核的[[远红外线|远红外线]]成像。<ref name="pr2014" />荧光DNA染色通常用于预测癌症。<ref name="pmid20800459">{{cite journal | vauthors = Klonisch T, Wark L, Hombach-Klonisch S, Mai S | title = Nuclear imaging in three dimensions: a unique tool in cancer research | journal = Annals of Anatomy - Anatomischer Anzeiger | volume = 192 | issue = 5 | pages = 292–301 | date = September 2010 | pmid = 20800459 | doi = 10.1016/j.aanat.2010.07.007 }}</ref>在{{le|琼脂糖|Agarose}}凝胶、{{le|荧光测定|Fluorometric assays}}和[[流式细胞术|流式细胞术]]中，甲基绿也可作为DNA的替代染色剂。<ref name="pr2014">{{cite journal | vauthors = Prieto D, Aparicio G, Morande PE, Zolessi FR | s2cid = 11094194 | title = A fast, low cost, and highly efficient fluorescent DNA labeling method using methyl green | journal = Histochemistry and Cell Biology | volume = 142 | issue = 3 | pages = 335–45 | date = September 2014 | pmid = 24671497 | doi = 10.1007/s00418-014-1215-0 }}</ref><ref name="pmid25993383">{{cite journal | vauthors = Prieto D, Aparicio G, Machado M, Zolessi FR | title = Application of the DNA-specific stain methyl green in the fluorescent labeling of embryos | journal = Journal of Visualized Experiments | issue = 99 | pages = e52769 | date = May 2015 | pmid = 25993383 | pmc = 4542129 | doi = 10.3791/52769 }}</ref>它还可以用作细胞的排除{{le|活力测定|Viability assay|活力}}染色剂。甲基绿和DNA的相互作用是非{{le|插层|intercalation (biochemistry)}}的，也就是说甲基绿没有插入DNA，而是和DNA的[[核酸双螺旋#大沟和小沟|大沟]]以[[静电|静电]]相互作用。<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Kim SK, Nordén B | title = Methyl green. A DNA major-groove binding drug | journal = FEBS Letters | volume = 315 | issue = 1 | pages = 61–4 | date = January 1993 | pmid = 8416812 | doi = 10.1016/0014-5793(93)81133-K | doi-access = free }}</ref>

在中性水溶液中用244或388 nm的光激发时，甲基绿就会分别在488或633 nm处产生荧光。DNA是否存在不会影响甲基绿的荧光性质。在中性水溶液中和DNA结合时，甲基绿也会在远红光中发出荧光，最大激发波长为633 nm，最大发射波长则为677 nm。<ref name="pr2014" />

商业的甲基绿试剂经常有[[结晶紫|结晶紫]]杂质，它们可以通过[[氯仿|氯仿]]萃取除去。<ref name="pr2014" />

